    "# Graded Part\n"

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 18,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def create_toroidal(k):\n",
    "    G=nx.Graph()\n",
    "    count = 0\n",
    "    mapping1 = {}\n",
    "    mapping2 = {}\n",
    "    for i in range(k):\n",
    "        for j in range(k):\n",
    "            mapping1[count] = (i,j)\n",
    "            mapping2[(i,j)] = count\n",
    "            G.add_node(count)\n",
    "            count +=1\n",
    "    for i in range(k):\n",
    "        for j in range(k):\n",
    "            if (i,j+1) in mapping2:\n",
    "                G.add_edge(mapping2[(i,j)],mapping2[i,j+1])\n",
    "            if (i,j-1) in mapping2:\n",
    "                G.add_edge(mapping2[(i,j)],mapping2[i,j-1])\n",
    "            if (i+1,j) in mapping2:\n",
    "                G.add_edge(mapping2[(i,j)],mapping2[i+1,j])\n",
    "            if (i-1,j) in mapping2:\n",
    "                G.add_edge(mapping2[(i,j)],mapping2[i-1,j])  \n",
    "    j = 0\n",
    "    for i in range(k):\n",
    "        G.add_edge(mapping2[(i,j)],mapping2[i,j+k-1])\n",
    "    i = 0\n",
    "    for j in range(k):\n",
    "        G.add_edge(mapping2[(i,j)],mapping2[i+k-1,j])\n",
    "    return G"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 19,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [

   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Harmonic function implementation"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 33,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def your_harmonic_function(G, label_name):\n",
    "    adjacency = [list(adj_nodes.keys()) for node, adj_nodes in G.adjacency()]\n",
    "    W = np.zeros((len(G.nodes), len(G.nodes)))\n",
    "    D = np.zeros((len(G.nodes), len(G.nodes)))\n",
    "    for i in range(len(adjacency)):\n",
    "        for j in adjacency[i]:\n",
    "            W[i, j] = 1\n",
    "            W[j, i] = 1\n",
    "        D[i, i] = sum(W[i,])\n",
    "\n",
    "    L = [i for i in G.nodes if label_name in G._node[i].keys()]\n",
    "    U = list(G.nodes-L)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    f = [[1, 0] if dic[label_name] == 'red' else [0, 1] for dic in [G._node[i] for i in L]]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    F = - np.linalg.inv(D[np.ix_(U, U)] - W[np.ix_(U, U)]).dot(W[np.ix_(U, L)]).dot(f)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    labeled_list = []\n",
    "    l = 0\n",
    "    u = 0\n",
    "    for i in range(len(G.nodes)):\n",
    "        if i in L:\n",
    "            label = 0 if f[l][0] > 0.5 else 1\n",
    "            labeled_list.append('blue' if label == 1 else 'red')\n",
    "            l += 1\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            label = 0 if F[u][0] > 0.5 else 1\n",
    "            labeled_list.append('blue' if label == 1 else 'red')\n",
    "            u += 1\n",
    "    return labeled_list\n",
    "    \n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 34,
   "metadata": {},

    "G = create_toroidal(16)  \n",

    "gpos = nx.spring_layout(G, iterations=200)\n",
    "node_color=['blue' if n == 0 else 'red' if n == 255 else 'gray' for n in G.nodes]\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))\n",
    "nx.draw(G, gpos, with_labels=False, node_size=200, node_color=node_color)\n",
    "plt.show()"
